{"tid":1164224,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[估國家] 預約過後足足等了2年才能看診；婦人體內瘜肉演變癌症第三期","createTime":"2019-05-21T02:19:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T02:38:44.000Z","uid":71237,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d4c521f3cba19792115a0e313f169f88c3a42bb2","tid":1164224,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T02:19:44.000Z","msg":"預約過後足足等了2年才能看診；加拿大婦人體內瘜肉演變癌症第三期需接受末期癌症治療。<br />\n<br />\n醫療資源緊絀是不同地方現正面對的問題。於加拿大就有一名婦人因身體不適預約看診，其後竟足足等了2年才被安排接受進一步檢查。原本的瘜肉更已演變成癌症第三期，實在是慘不忍賭。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大33歲婦人Inez Rudderham在社交網站發佈發表影片，指她早已預約家庭醫生，卻被拖了2年才能看診。於這2年內，她曾到不同醫院的急證室求助，但其個案卻沒有受到理會。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y6cn7t9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY6cn7t9.png&h=e66efae1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就醫時，瘜肉已變成肛門癌第三期<br />\n<br />\n經過了2年的等待，終於輪到她看診時，原來她體內的瘜肉早已演變成肛門癌第三期。而因為治療嚴重耽誤，癌細胞亦已擴散，她邢要接受末期癌症治療。過程中需接受多達30多次的骨盆放射性治療，令她終身失去生育能力。<br />\n<br />\n這一次看診耽誤，不但令她需要面對末期癌症的痛苦，亦令其心理壓力倍增，但就連預約心理治療師也須等到7月才能看診」。<br />\n<br />\n影片引起醫療界關注<br />\n<br />\n影片自上傳到社交網站Facebook至今，已累積超過12萬個分享。除引起網友熱烈討論外，亦引了當地醫生團體的關注，坦言加拿大家庭醫生數目嚴重短缺，當地省長也承諾會找相關單位幫助Inez Rudderham的狀況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://medicalinspire.com/web/posts/34340\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedicalinspire.com%2Fweb%2Fposts%2F34340&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbf8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=7ed4d17a\" target=\"_blank\">https://medicalinspire.com/web/posts/34340</a><br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/marilyn.inez/videos/10156155486545812\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmarilyn.inez%2Fvideos%2F10156155486545812&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbf8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=f354a917\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/marilyn.inez/videos/10156155486545812</a>"},{"pid":"2cae67289a2ad016ac2812db1af6d4e4c2494d4f","tid":1164224,"uid":164372,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T02:20:19.000Z","msg":"以為係香港添"},{"pid":"5a597ada632e7eba1be1602b58c6c0c3db7ab3a1","tid":1164224,"uid":160063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T02:20:45.000Z","msg":"應該冇人估得中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afd9c9c3fdccb9e2850afda2b3afdefae5afd799","tid":1164224,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T02:22:52.000Z","msg":"又話加拿大醫療好好， 所以個個移民過去"},{"pid":"eba3e18f4f40446f418ebf9b0083635ee8734827","tid":1164224,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5a597ada632e7eba1be1602b58c6c0c3db7ab3a1","tid":1164224,"uid":160063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T02:20:45.000Z","msg":"應該冇人估得中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T02:28:05.000Z","msg":"剛剛搵多啲關於加拿大的資料，發現同香港差唔多。<br />\n<br />\nThe recommended wait times for hip and knee replacement are themselves excessive &mdash; 182 days or six months &mdash; and 112 days or almost four months for cataract surgery.<br />\n<a href=\"https://torontosun.com/opinion/editorials/editorial-canadas-medical-wait-times-are-unacceptable\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftorontosun.com%2Fopinion%2Feditorials%2Feditorial-canadas-medical-wait-times-are-unacceptable&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbf8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=49b2005d\" target=\"_blank\">https://torontosun.com/opinion/editorials/editorial-canadas-medical-wait-times-are-unacceptable</a><br />\n<br />\nSome patients can wait up to 20 hours to see a doctor at the Chalmers emergency room<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/new-brunswick/doctors-emergency-room-dr-everett-chalmers-regional-hospital-1.5139857\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fcanada%2Fnew-brunswick%2Fdoctors-emergency-room-dr-everett-chalmers-regional-hospital-1.5139857&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbf8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=6fb96bc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/new-brunswick/doctors-emergency-room-dr-everett-chalmers-regional-hospital-1.5139857</a><br />\n<br />\nWait times for heart imaging tests reach 5-year high in Winnipeg<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/manitoba/wait-times-heart-imaging-1.5133713\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fcanada%2Fmanitoba%2Fwait-times-heart-imaging-1.5133713&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbf8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=e4f1d707\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/manitoba/wait-times-heart-imaging-1.5133713</a>"},{"pid":"3a334788fc81feede239c603c717d9a29a729710","tid":1164224,"uid":186177,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T02:30:49.000Z","msg":"睇嚟加拿大都要開放中国医生免試執葉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8d0d4b59862f3393e4dbd15a2b7e8e442e7a219","tid":1164224,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T02:32:00.000Z","msg":"估錯國家"},{"pid":"e12873442df3f73a8c9955f09009c93bd5f0529b","tid":1164224,"uid":228223,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T02:33:03.000Z","msg":"喺英國隨時拖到第四期晚期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ae0bb75d84c0997c0fb35c32b036f31f02555d","tid":1164224,"uid":126831,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T02:33:58.000Z","msg":"外國地方大，資源唔集中。如果有咩大手術，而你住係好遠&alpha;re&alpha;,就要去返大城市先做到。好多時死左都冇人知。其實香港有問題，外國都一樣，不過香港係嚴重d咁解。"},{"pid":"5b6da280af38705a624d9a968aee8dde1f5c4c0f","tid":1164224,"uid":228346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e6ae0bb75d84c0997c0fb35c32b036f31f02555d","tid":1164224,"uid":126831,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T02:33:58.000Z","msg":"外國地方大，資源唔集中。如果有咩大手術，而你住係好遠&alpha;re&alpha;,就要去返大城市先做到。好多時死左都冇人知。其實香港有問題